OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA rather
OL,6,Fcloudy evening with a few showery
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain spreading north.
OL,8,FRain will turn occasionally heavy for
OL,9,Fa time across Caithness and Sutherland
OL,10,Fbefore turning generally drier later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA rather cloudy start to
OL,13,Fthe morning with patchy light rain.
OL,14,FTurning brighter through the day with
OL,15,Fsunny spells and scattered showers,
OL,16,Fone or two on the heavier side.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
